{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extra funding for SEND holiday clubs",
        "additional_details": "Due to the lack of support during school holidays for parents with SEND children, is making it difficult for parents to go to work or even have a break. By providing funding and extra support during the school holidays will not only benefit SEND children but also benefit the parents. It will improve both health and wellbeing for both.",
        "background": "Provide funding to allow more holidays clubs for SEND children, so parents can go to work!",
